  "description": "The two-chamber refrigerator, representing the Bosch Serie 6 comfort class line, belongs to models with an increased body width (86 cm), which makes it the best choice for spacious kitchens and large families. The useful volume of the device reaches 619 liters, of which 140 liters fall on the freezer. The latter provides two drawers of different sizes, is characterized by powerful freezing (up to 20 kg per day) and long-term preservation of cold during power outages (up to 30 hours). The 479-liter refrigerator compartment received 4 open shelves and four drawers of the VitaFresh plus freshness zone, where you can store various products, from fish or meat to vegetables and fruits. For ease of management and temperature control, the Bosch KGN86AI30 refrigerator has two cooling circuits and an external touch panel. Here you can turn on fast freezing or cooling, activate the holiday mode or lock the controls to protect against children. Other features include the Full No Frost automatic defrost system, economical energy consumption (class A ++), as well as moderate noise (up to 42 dB).",
